      "name": "PIV velocity field comparison — FDA pump",
      "description": "Comparison of CFD-predicted velocity fields against particle image velocimetry measurements in the FDA generic centrifugal pump at 3 operating points. Mean absolute error in axial velocity < 8% across all measurement planes.",
      "wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-piv-measurements"
    },
    {
