      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Hemolysis index comparison against in-vitro experiments",
      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against in-vitro measurements at 5 flow-speed combinations. Predictions fall within ±25% of measured NIH values; Monte Carlo 95th-percentile bounds overlap experimental uncertainty intervals at 4 of 5 operating points.",
      "wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/data/hemolysis-in-vitro-experiments"
