      "rationale": "Relative error computed at 5 operating points; experimental uncertainty estimated from repeat trials (n=3 per point). Simulation uncertainty from Monte Carlo only; numerical discretization uncertainty not combined into total simulation uncertainty. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
