      "rationale": "NIH is the primary regulatory metric; however, the Giersiepen-Wurzinger model is calibrated on Couette-flow data and its applicability to complex 3-D pump flows is not formally justified in the validation report. Achieved level 2 against required level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the validation activities to the COU",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
