      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification for the choice of hemolysis constitutive model (power-law vs. mechanistic) and turbulence closure must be provided with quantitative evidence of suitability for VAD flow regimes.",
      "rationale": "Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law model selected without formal comparison to alternative mechanistic models. SST k-omega turbulence closure applied without documented justification for transitional flow regime in pump passages. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
